devdoc.details: Implementation of Ocean DataTokens Factory *      Factory deploys DataToken proxy contracts.     New DataToken proxy contracts are links to the template contract's bytecode.      Proxy contract functionality is based on Ocean Protocol custom implementation of ERC1167 standard.

params._template: refers to the address of a deployed DataToken contract.
